channel.description:
[center]Deidara-Scape 718/742
~ Construction ~
It is under devolopment but trainable. you are able to make some furniture. Don't be upset over it please, we will continue to work on construction.
~ Farming ~
Farming is partly coded and mostly works, except for saving, example ; If a player was farming and there were half done and they relogged it would most likely disappear. We are sorry if you get upset over the problem with saving for farming, but we will later on try and find a way around it.
